<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Geleceğin Finans Analizi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --main: #6366f1; --bg: #0f172a; --glass: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7); --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        body { background: var(--bg); color: #f8fafc; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; margin: 0; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* Arka Plan Işımaları */
        .blob { position: absolute; width: 500px; height: 500px; background: var(--main); filter: blur(120px); opacity: 0.15; z-index: -1; border-radius: 50%; }
        .blob-1 { top: -200px; right: -100px; }
        .blob-2 { bottom: -200px; left: -100px; }

        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 30px 0; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .logo span { color: var(--main); }

        .hero { text-align: center; padding: 100px 0 60px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -3px; margin: 0; line-height: 1; }
        .hero p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 25px 0; }

        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; margin-top: 50px; }
        .card { 
            background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid var(--border); 
            padding: 40px; border-radius: 30px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.3, 1); 
        }
        .card:hover { transform: scale(1.03); border-color: var(--main); background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05); }
        .card i { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--main); margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .card h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 10px 0; }
        .card p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }

        footer { margin-top: 100px; padding: 40px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b; }
        .f-links a { color: #94a3b8; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .f-links a:hover { color: var(--main); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-2"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a>
            <a href="/bilgi/iletisim" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600;">Destek</a>
        </nav>

        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Finansal Zeka.<br><span>Sıfır Hata.</span></h1>
            <p>Karmaşık hesaplamaları saniyeler içinde profesyonel raporlara dönüştürün.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="grid">
            <a href="/kredi" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i>
                <h3>Kredi Analizi</h3>
                <p>Bankaların gizli maliyetlerini açığa çıkarın ve en uygun teklifi bulun.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mevduat" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h3>Mevduat Rehberi</h3>
                <p>Birikimleriniz için en yüksek reel getiriyi sağlayan bankaları listeleyin.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/kredi-limit" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-check"></i>
                <h3>Limit Skorlama</h3>
                <p>Mevcut finansal verilerinizle çekebileceğiniz kredi limitini görün.</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <div class="f-links">
                <a href="/bilgi/hakkimizda">Kurumsal</a>
                <a href="/bilgi/kvkk">Gizlilik</a>
                <a href="/bilgi/kosullar">Kullanım</a>
            </div>
            <p>© 2026 Hesap360. Profesyonel Finans Çözümleri.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
